type":"example","text":"A：I feel that Tom and I hold completely different ideas. （我觉得汤"},{"type":"text","text":"姆和我的观点完全不同。）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：Maybe it is due to the cultural difference between East and West."},{"type":"text","text":"（或许是因为东西方文化的差异。）"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 2"},{"type":"example","text":"A：What's the matter with you? （你怎么啦？）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：Nothing, I am just a little homesick. （没什么，我就是有点想"},{"type":"text","text":"家。）"}]}]}